<chapter xml:id="VoiceLeadingSeventhChords">
    <title>Voice Leading Seventh Chords</title>
    <section xml:id="VoiceLeadingSeventhChordsIntro">
        <title>Voice Leading Seventh Chords</title>
        <p>There is one general rule for voice leading any seventh chord: resolve the 7th of the chord down by step. All other voices should move smoothly to the nearest chord tone in a voicing containing the appropriate doubling.</p>
        <principle xml:id="voice-leading-seventh-chords-principle">
            <title>7th chords</title>
            <statement>
                <p>Resolve the 7th of a 7th chord down by step.</p>
            </statement>
        </principle>
